# Ilirea
>Capital of the [[Locations/Broddring Empire\|Broddring Kingdom]]

Ilirea was the last [[Races/Elves\|elven]] stronghold located outside of [[Locations/Du Weldenvarden\|Du Weldenvarden]] before it was seized by [[Characters/Galbatorix\|Galbatorix]] and renamed Ur√ª'baen (also called the Black City by dissenters). It served as the capital for the [[Locations/Broddring Empire\|Broddring Empire]], and after the conclusion of the [[Events/Rider War\|Rider War]], it was restored to its former name, Ilirea, and made the capital of the [[Locations/Broddring Empire\|Kingdom]].
